 I am planning to do the late model gas tank retrofit into my 63. I had a tank from a 76 already on hand but
the outlets don't look quite right. On this tank there are two outlets that are positioned tword the bottom
right front as looking at the tank with the filler neck to the right. Is the cutout in my 63 going to line up?
